  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 2 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  mandatory: 0
  lines:
  - AN UPDATE ON THE VIRUS
  - We have been able to confirm a second symptom of the virus.
  - Infected individuals will experience severe back acne alongside the previously
    disclosed rash on the arm.
  - Citizens who experience only 1 of the 2 known symptoms are believed to not be
    infected, and will not need to contact anyone regarding this issue.
